{"tid":2053673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抖音TikTok戰線？？？","createTime":"2020-06-06T12:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T12:40:34.000Z","uid":7835,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3b235e005e412a1a0d1a4fbfc9eed7b0e7f2e821","tid":2053673,"uid":7835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"雖然抖音係共產黨所擁有<br />\n但我哋都不能否認<br />\n佢的確喺短時間內獲得巨大嘅成功<br />\n<br />\n起初有呢個諗法<br />\n係因為我幾個補習學生日撚日都玩抖音<br />\n入邊大多數都係冇營養戇鳩片<br />\n但佢久唔久會滲啲藍絲WeChat瘋傳嗰啲content farm片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長年累月咁接收呢啲資訊<br />\n加上屋企係藍<br />\n我嗰幾個學生四五年級已經藍到黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抖音文宣戰線值唔值得做真係見仁見智<br />\n通過抖音 我哋可以真正走出同溫層<br />\n接觸到好多俾中共大外宣洗晒腦嘅小學雞<br />\n我只係做咗幾日<br />\n已經有幾個小朋友PM我 話佢未睇過呢啲片，有啲差人真係好衰等等<br />\n總而言之 抖音戰線即係將精神同心思投資落香港嘅下一代身上<br />\n效果一定有 但要人長期做嘅覺悟<br />\n但我個人認為如果可以令一個小朋友由深藍變番中立少少<br />\n呢條戰線已經算冇白費心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得我傻都唔緊要<br />\n開呢個post唔係想鼓勵大家join<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而係我喺抖音整嗰d鳩片<br />\n因爲主要for小學雞睇<br />\n內容顯淺，主旨清晰而且夠短<br />\n好適合喺WhatsApp send俾淺藍長輩睇<br />\n所以順便開埋一個YouTube Channel放片<br />\n大家有需要可以subscribe, download啲片落嚟用<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ta4trnc44p8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTa4trnc44p8&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdxyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=80bc2970\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ta4trnc44p8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8f9043e031788e3f5494755a9d8402a0b564f070","tid":2053673,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:59:27.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"316300ca82ca3154ad751c3e5e4b6bb81d959f0c","tid":2053673,"uid":94613,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:00:12.000Z","msg":"咁都冇比人ban?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 巴打咁玩記得拎第二部手機玩<br />\ndata直上北京 <br />\n因間比國安睇中就唔好啦"},{"pid":"f6d556f2a3b42384eb0d85d131aea1c348d6a1b6","tid":2053673,"uid":150483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"唔可以話滲透<br />\n師夷其技以制夷<br />\n<br />\n佢哋搞掂連登，就係將所有野拉到極端<br />\n例如，抖音拍飲食-奶茶聯盟，拍vlog-笑韓國瑜，講支共滲透<br />\n<br />\n直至對家有反應就代表中計，最好愈搞愈大咁"},{"pid":"560a0c52ae08f1a2e3dcc5c03d1fd7b4a416b549","tid":2053673,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"玩tiktok用鬼機"},{"pid":"2738ba508fb884d738767fa5a91bb059b2bae511","tid":2053673,"uid":150483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"316300ca82ca3154ad751c3e5e4b6bb81d959f0c","tid":2053673,"uid":94613,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:00:12.000Z","msg":"咁都冇比人ban?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 巴打咁玩記得拎第二部手機玩<br />\ndata直上北京 <br />\n因間比國安睇中就唔好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"善用奶茶聯盟<br />\n<br />\n既然外國人有心一齊恥笑，咁咪一齊行動<br />\n好似其他任務都係<br />\n<br />\n雖然個名好兒戲，但支共一樣係咁而成功大外宣<br />\n呢個聯盟發大黎搞可以好有力量，除非你放棄網絡戰"},{"pid":"d42296b6dc198f2d3ebc2a304f98f15c0936daf0","tid":2053673,"uid":7835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"316300ca82ca3154ad751c3e5e4b6bb81d959f0c","tid":2053673,"uid":94613,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:00:12.000Z","msg":"咁都冇比人ban?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 巴打咁玩記得拎第二部手機玩<br />\ndata直上北京 <br />\n因間比國安睇中就唔好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"暫時未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收到！多謝關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f1f7a3f983b3b7b5b47ff3c091de00df1c6c8f","tid":2053673,"uid":7835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"560a0c52ae08f1a2e3dcc5c03d1fd7b4a